==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Black Rod
<hw>Black" Rod`</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>. <sd>(a)</sd> <def>the usher to the
Chapter of the Garter, so called from the <ets>black rod</ets> which he
carries. He is of the king's chamber, and also usher to the House of
Lords.</def> <mark>[Eng.]</mark> <sd>(b)</sd> <def>An usher in the
legislature of British colonies.</def> <rj><au>Cowell.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Committed to the custody of the <qex>Black Rod</qex>.</q>
<rj><qau>Macaulay.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Blackroot</ent>⟦br⟧
